東南臨海有都會曰祿奈（或作祿賴，一作龍奈，一作農耐），占城之故都也。南境臨海有都會曰柬埔寨，真臘之故都也。閩廣商船，每歲往來貿易。別國商船入港，譏防甚嚴。榷稅亦重，諸國惡其煩苛，故市舶罕有至者。所產者，番木、沉楠諸香，鉛、錫、桂皮、象牙、燕窩、魚翅之類。其入貢，由廣西之太平府入關，不由海道（安南本中國地，諸書言之綦詳，故不多贅）。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:46:04.000Z","msg":"越南泰國全世界都公認 <br />\n英文係Thailand唔係Siam <br />\n台灣都係咁叫<br />\n反而係寮國唔係老撾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:50:11.000Z","msg":"順帶一提暹羅(Siam)改名為泰國(Thailand)<br />\n係拉瑪五世西化運動其中一項改革<br />\n同日本明治維新江戶改稱東京一樣"},{"pid":"c73a3c2f0f1acc77305f424ab8e8d2810727cae2","tid":1676017,"uid":237562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:51:06.000Z","msg":"不要說東三省<br />\n<br />\n說滿州國"},{"pid":"31858259bb3921291beeab576dcfb1eac477ec47","tid":1676017,"uid":85327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:51:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a226389ba8f8bede1d19a32f8060ed7257f323f0","tid":1676017,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:51:38.000Z","msg":"Beijing?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBeiping<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d9cd15fd08e50d29e050eb58c088a4bfb0829ef","tid":1676017,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fa19f71117bfac33095f005b4acfa42aca862b0","tid":1676017,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15982e25d9f72de89c7e2a32b9e315fc73f3d4ce","tid":1676017,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c08de4ff2801065f994f83cfbe704add64a2b83","tid":1676017,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:01:39.000Z","msg":"點解有問題？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:08:33.000Z","msg":"吐蕃係古稱，源自直譯<br />\n西藏一詞源自滿文"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:15:15.000Z","msg":"西藏接受得到對滿清既臣服<br />\n我地又冇乜角色出聲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:52:49.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n<br />\n達賴同清皇帝有藩屬之類關係<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以根本